
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Conv as Conversation Service
    participant ConvDB as Conversation DB
    participant RabbitMQ as RabbitMQ Broker
    participant Chatbot as Chatbot Service
    participant ChatbotDB as Chatbot DB
    participant R2 as R2 Object Storage

    User->>+Conv: POST /code-conversation-service/chats/share (Kèm chatId & lastMessageId)
    Conv->>+ConvDB: Kiểm tra quyền sở hữu Chat
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: OK

    Conv->>+ConvDB: INSERT Share (status='PENDING') & INSERT Outbox (ShareGeneratedEvent)
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: Commit Transaction (Atomic)

    Conv-->>-User: HTTP 201 Created (Trả về shareId & shareUrl tạm thời)

    Note over Conv, RabbitMQ: Cron job OutboxRelay quét DB định kỳ gửi event
    Conv->>+ConvDB: SELECT PENDING OutboxEvents
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: Danh sách events
    Conv->>+RabbitMQ: Publish 'ShareGeneratedEvent' (Queue: share_generated)
    RabbitMQ-->>-Conv: Ack
    Conv->>+ConvDB: UPDATE Outbox status='DONE'
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: OK

    RabbitMQ-->>+Chatbot: Consume 'ShareGeneratedEvent'
    Chatbot->>+ChatbotDB: Query tin nhắn của Chat đến lastMessageId
    ChatbotDB-->>-Chatbot: Danh sách tin nhắn
    Note over Chatbot: Xử lý build nội dung chat thành JSONL

    Chatbot->>+R2: Upload file JSONL (Key: shared_chats/{userId}/{shareId}.jsonl)
    R2-->>-Chatbot: Trả về file_url
    Chatbot->>+ChatbotDB: Lưu thông tin Share và Version mới để đồng bộ
    ChatbotDB-->>-Chatbot: OK

    Chatbot->>+RabbitMQ: Publish 'ShareUploadCompletedEvent' (Queue: share_upload_completed)
    RabbitMQ-->>-Chatbot: Ack
    Chatbot-->>-RabbitMQ: Acknowledge (Hoàn thành Task gốc)

    RabbitMQ-->>+Conv: Consume 'ShareUploadCompletedEvent'
    Conv->>+ConvDB: Cập nhật Share (status='ACTIVE', fileUrl=fileUrl)
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: OK
    Conv-->>-RabbitMQ: Acknowledge
